							<body  ><div class="section"><p class="Speech"><a name="time_20160922 10:07:57" ></a><strong>Hon NANAIA MAHUTA (Labour—Hauraki-Waikato)</strong>: </p><p class="IndentMarginalone">[Authorised Te Reo text to be inserted by the Hansard Office.]</p><p class="IndentMarginalone">[Authorised translation to be inserted by the Hansard Office.]</p></div></body>
